{"id":5629,"date":"2017-03-20T16:01:57","date_gmt":"2017-03-20T16:01:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/mercantile.wordpress.org\/?page_id=5629"},"modified":"2025-04-11T16:22:47","modified_gmt":"2025-04-11T16:22:47","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/mercantile.wordpress.org\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Mercantile Store is the official swag store of the WordPress project. Show the world your love of WordPress with cool gear you can wear, accessorize with, tote, and more. With new products added regularly, there\u2019s something for everyone\u2014whether you are new to WordPress or a long-time fan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>The WordPress Swag Store is hosted by Automattic. All profits will be donated to the <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/wordpressfoundation.org\/\"><em>WordPress Foundation<\/em><\/a><em>.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\"><summary><strong>U.S ORDERS<\/strong><\/summary>\n<p>You can expect to receive your order within 3-7 business days once your order has shipped. Tracking information will be sent to the email provided at checkout.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\"><summary><strong>INTERNATIONAL ORDERS<\/strong><\/summary>\n<p>You can expect to receive your order within 1- 4 weeks depending on the destination country. Tracking information will be sent to the email provided at checkout.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All international customers are subject to the customs laws, duties, and taxes of the destination country. If your package is returned for any reason, you will be notified by email. If you do not respond within two weeks we will return the item(s) into our stock and refund you the amount of the order. Shipping and credit card transaction fees are non-refundable.<\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\"><summary><strong>RETURNS\/EXCHANGES<\/strong><\/summary>\n<p>We hope you love your new WordPress swag! We stand behind everything we sell and want you to be happy with your new purchase. Should you find any issues with the quality of your new item please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:mercantile@wordpress.org\">mercantile@wordpress.org<\/a>. <em>Shipping and credit card transaction fees are non-refundable.&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\"><summary><strong>BULK ORDERS<\/strong><\/summary>\n<p>Do you accommodate large bulk orders?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Possibly! If you need more than 10 of any product, please contact <a href=\"mailto:mercantile@wordpress.org\">mercantile@wordpress.org<\/a> with the product, specific quantity, and sizes that you need. Some items may have to be special-ordered. Bulk orders may be eligible for discount pricing.<\/p>\n<\/details>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Mercantile Store is the official swag store of the WordPress project. Show the world your love of WordPress with cool gear you can wear, accessorize with, tote, and more. With new products added regularly, there\u2019s something for everyone\u2014whether you are new to WordPress or a long-time fan. The WordPress Swag Store is hosted by [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":30,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-5629","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.1.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>About - WordPress Swag Store<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/mercantile.wordpress.org\/about\/\"